{"tid":1459722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"既然大家都話有鬼…咁點解唔一齊捉鬼？","createTime":"2019-08-12T19:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T20:04:16.000Z","uid":215408,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"75ea7d553811e23a4492a1c8af2b933e8a87985b","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:34:28.000Z","msg":"對於近2次或更耐之前發夢，開始話鬼鬼地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、有鬼fake前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、有鬼做分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、我們中出了一個叛徒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解我地唔整個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">捉鬼敢死隊</span></span>呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反正啲鬼唔show委任證<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />證明唔到佢地係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咁我地捉到既話對佢地做咩都唔關黑驚事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果之後發夢仲見到啲疑似黑驚既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地特徵有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">特別煩躁</span>；谷到一肚火唔知係咪太耐冇得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又ot咗咁耐仲未收得工，問兩問會發脾氣叫你收聲然後敗走<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶住耳機</span>；呢樣唔駛講啦大家都明<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇公安高層order邊會衝出黎柒呀，比人圍就有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應該三至四個人一齊行</span>；鍾意群體行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方便裏應外合<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大大隻隻， 牙牙咋咋</span></span>；唔係邊㩒得住義士<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見到記者會掉頭走or有啲抗拒</span></span>；呢個有可能啲點錯相，因為我地實有人唔鍾意上鏡，小心認錯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我暫時淨係知咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果巴絲們覺得有錯或漏既可以再加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位安全發夢，抗爭成功之後約定各位喺煲底除低面罩，互相擁抱<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿忘初衷</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ccff1a556642d86bf2b17dc05794024121af7d29","tid":1459722,"uid":14262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:34:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寧可輸給極權 絕不自我放棄！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一日場仗未打完，都唔可以認命！<br />\n所有想自殺想放棄既人聽住，同我地堅持下去！<br />\n依家未係心灰既時候，<br />\n如果場革命係因為放棄而輸<br />\n仲點對得住過世義士及被捕義士！<br />\n仲邊有面目做人！<br />\n同我地打埋場仗佢！<br />\n<br />\n<em>（幫推及傳遞訊息，一個手足不能少）</em>"},{"pid":"9daf594d95c159b8a41b104639be45cc15277d4a","tid":1459722,"uid":19055,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:36:13.000Z","msg":"唔洗捉<br />\n等黑警擺陣前就要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a558cbf4d45c171d7313e605472ad71af3ecdeac","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:36:19.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ca5320c6133badb80ce737687f4f93d0b52c39","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:36:30.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"56ef9bbd6bbeda5ed19c382ebaba9f0316a5f081","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:36:40.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"2961e91e0b6cd493c2e0fa74939d54e23a4c9d5b","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:37:00.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"8eee387d5241aab44c36d4acf4cd26e5622c2738","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:37:13.000Z","msg":"七"},{"pid":"049b1f56cdeacc12b73bcac1e202dce039922a50","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:38:32.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"f3e3dbe4975f61eb4721eac2b8a4e231240e02ab","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:38:45.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"195984c560c6b4b58a981a558c62af6a33973a77","tid":1459722,"uid":305822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:38:54.000Z","msg":"sorry小妹借位跪求推<br />\n突發！ 點解冇人講816攬炒啦你老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456799\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee421d90624beade0e5fac2a502bffb997d406fd","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:38:55.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"ae37f4ce958863fba1e33d3e96fd1dea2c4cf12f","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:39:16.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"6eb52accc0702570abccc227439239bd669e7b63","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:39:27.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"6e1fd8a3cee14c4496d17987a5a096d315419dfc","tid":1459722,"uid":215408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"36979a15185ca94910b85e11b23c984e90935e59","tid":1459722,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T19:39:46.000Z","msg":"大叫二五狗死全家"},{"pid":"6e61047ad6fe762a034c8edb6afd8b